            <li><title>March 27</title>
	    <p>Withdrawal Deadline (5pm)</p></li>
            <li><title>April 25</title>
	    <p>Classes End</p></li>
            <li><title>April 25 - May 2</title>
	    <p>Final Exams (see Registrar page for schedule)</p></li>
            <li><title>May 2</title>
	    <p>Last day of semester</p></li>
          </dl>
          </p>

          <p>
            More at the
            <url
                href="https://www.gvsu.edu/registrar/academiccalendar.htm">
              University academic calendar.
            </url>
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            This course is subject to these
            <url href="http://www.gvsu.edu/coursepolicies/">
              GVSU policies.
            </url>
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            In the (hopefully unlikely) event that the university
            moves all classes online, or if I am ill or unable to come
            to campus, I will contact you through a Blackboard
            announcement and let you know of a plan.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            I reserve the right to make changes to this syllabus.  Any
            changes made after the syllabus is first distributed
